Class UISocketNotification

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wisc.trace.uch.util.socket.AbstractUISocketElement
      • edu.wisc.trace.uch.util.socket.UISocketNotification
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IUISocketElement

    public class UISocketNotification
extends AbstractUISocketElement
    UISocketNotification is the notification variant of UISocketElement. It provides the functionality for acknowledging notifications.
    Version:
    $Revision: 798 $
    Author:
    Parikshit Thakur & Team, Trace R&D Center
